ingin mengembalikannya?

54
00:02:49,119 --> 00:02:51,720
Apa?

55
00:02:52,389 --> 00:02:57,060
Apa maksudmu kau 
akan menukar hidup...

56
00:02:57,060 --> 00:03:00,790
