00:20:58,741 --> 00:21:01,680
Apa yang terjadi?
Ae Ri! Bangun, Ae Ri!

296
00:21:01,910 --> 00:21:04,040
Ae Ri! Ae Ri!

297
00:21:04,546 --> 00:21:06,410
